    "en": {
      "title": "SLFP opposes awarding millions in damages for \u2018political revenge victims\u2019",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan Freedom Party (SLFP) yesterday said it will oppose any attempt by the Government to pay millions in damages to several Government officials and institutional heads over claims they were politically victimized by",
        "The party release issued with the signature of its Chairman Maithripala Sirisena also noted it was unsuitable to portray the persons as \u2018political victims\u2019 as on observation of the list of names, it is evident the decisions were taken based on judicial proceedings.",
        "Sirisena also said the party opposes any decision made by the current Government to make payments amounting to millions in damages at a time where Sri Lanka is facing a severe economic crisis. \u201cThe Government\u2019s priority now must be to save both the country and the people from the economic crisis and not waste public funds in this manner,\u201d he said."
      ],
